{"tid":1286812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兄弟姊妹們 區議會選舉要有你同我（一齊到各區做助選 ）","createTime":"2019-07-05T03:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T04:27:58.000Z","uid":172300,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"526487dddb8f10d579fc4b68afb9be58fd7177ff","tid":1286812,"uid":172300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:30:13.000Z","msg":"不如一齊分析 23區 民陣派點可以勝出.<br />\n<br />\n生命可貴 其實我地係充滿希望 ， 如果有失望感/無能感請轉化為資料 搜集 同分析 動力。 <br />\n<br />\n我地一定要 贏<br />\n<br />\n利申：人生第一次就選民"},{"pid":"7c956f59a34302d1fa7cf49219065a082fda8aac","tid":1286812,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:30:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b532c2b224f3ce8489fa73cdd76f36e41e33eedb","tid":1286812,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:30:57.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ee6658df80b4897df1cb7ffc5a8ab3577a668b0","tid":1286812,"uid":266207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:33:48.000Z","msg":"一team助選，一team踩對家場。分開做<br />\n建制擺檔，見一檔踩一檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f528af6defc2623462c15cea6c592380afa249","tid":1286812,"uid":172300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:34:11.000Z","msg":"其實我地好多野做到 可能我發貼唔太識修飾 。 <br />\n<br />\n呢到每個兄弟姊